name: Timesheets
body:
Timesheets is an app that makes time tracking incredibly easy.

### Features

* precise tracking down to the millisecond
* flexible reporting
* GitHub and [waffle.io](https://waffle.io/) integration
* makes you pancakes in the morning


### Authors and Contributors

Timesheets is maintained by [Burkhard Reffeling](https://github.com/hardchor). Find me on twitter [@BurkhardR](https://twitter.com/BurkhardR).


### Found an issue?

Having trouble with Timesheets? Read through the [README](https://github.com/hardchor/timesheets#readme), [file an issue](https://github.com/hardchor/timesheets/issues) or [open a pull request](https://github.com/hardchor/timesheets/pulls)!
